   AUTODIE Corp. (Grand Rapids, Mich.) -- J. Thomas Winters,
48 years old, was named to the new position of executive vice
president and chief operating officer of this maker of auto
parts. Mr. Winters was corporate vice president of sales and
marketing.
</LP>
