   UNICOMP Inc. (Richardson, Texas) -- Ronald G. Brown,
former executive vice president of the Spreen Financial
Corp., was named president and chief operating officer of
this computer reseller, succeeding James H. Smith, who
resigned.
</LP>
<TEXT>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>
WSJ900726-0120
