<LP>
   AST Research Inc. reported record fiscal fourth-quarter
net income of $15.2 million, or $1.18 a share, compared with
$2.5 million, or 21 cents a share for the year-ago quarter.
   The Irvine, Calif.-based company said revenue for the
quarter reached $151.8 million, from $123.5 million last
